<p><strong>We are always looking for new group members with passion, talent, and grit! .</strong></p>

<p>You will have the chance to work on the grand challenges of Internet of Things and Cyber Security. 
You will be involved in determining the important and interesting research questions, creating and improving instrumental setups, performing experiments, and making discoveries.</p>

